# 💡 请从 campaign.http 获取一个处于 Active 状态的项目 ID
@campaign_id = 123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174001

### 1. 发起投资 (Create Order)
# @name create_order
POST {{base_url}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{user_token}}

{
    "campaign_id": "{{campaign_id}}",
    "amount": 500000
}

### 2. 再次发起投资 (验证并发累加)
POST {{base_url}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{user_token}}

{
    "campaign_id": "{{campaign_id}}",
    "amount": 100000
}

### 3. 查看项目详情 (验证金额是否增长)
GET {{base_url}}/campaigns/{{campaign_id}}
